  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cardiac Output (amount of blood pumped by the heart in one minute) will be measured using the
      new COstatus(R) system and these values will be compared with cardiac output values measured
      by other methods such as thermodilution. Blood volumes measured by the COstatus(R) system
      will also be recorded.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
